data.description: First time on the market custom built for sellers and a rare find VA assumable loan with low interest rates!!! Country living at its best! Just 5-15 minutes away from shopping and dining. This wonderful Nature friendly property is completely fenced and with almost an acre potentially room for an additional guest home, work shop or let your imagination's to be explored. Great room open concept.  Spacious Master bedroom. Relaxing outside covered decks in the shade. Paved parking for guests plus extra gravel road for possible RV/boat parking etc. Showings require 24 hr. notice for Thursdays through Sundays 11-5 only.
